QtPlugin provides CMake targets:

    find_package(QtPlugin CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE QtPlugin::Core)

Available components:
- Core: Essential plugin system functionality
- Security: Security validation and permission management
- Network: Network plugin support (requires network feature)
- UI: User interface plugin support (requires ui feature)

Example usage:
    find_package(QtPlugin CONFIG REQUIRED COMPONENTS Core Security)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE QtPlugin::Core QtPlugin::Security)

For pkg-config users:
    pkg-config --cflags --libs qtplugin
